In order to access these (our offers) you must meet the following criteria:
help us spread the news by inviting friends to use the Beez platform as well.
have a minimum number of purchases made through the platform.
make available in our platform the amount you need to pay for your chosen deal.
Check the progress of your goals with the help of the "sweet deal" indicators.
